### Crear detalle de pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/order-details
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderId": 1,
    "productId": 3,
    "quantity": 2
}

### Obtener todos los detalles de pedidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/order-details
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un detalle por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/order-details/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar cantidad del detalle
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order-details/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quantity": 5
}

### Eliminar detalle
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/order-details/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
